    • Method Detail

      • matches

        default boolean matches(DynamicCommandResponse other)
        Checks for a duplicate response and upon matching, the matched response will be cancelled. Implementations of this method must be able to accept null and return false upon doing so.
        Parameters:
        other - a response that has been sent
        Returns:
        true if the other response should be cancelled to make way for this response.
